790
01:00:03,820 --> 01:00:14,480
We figured this out and weren't ready to pay 30-40 thousand dollars to make this conductor — if, of course, you don't need to make a lot of this alloy.

791
01:00:14,480 --> 01:00:23,220
But if you needed it for a research program, or you have your own metallurgical lab, then of course you can make them and run experiments with them.

792
01:00:23,640 --> 01:00:24,500
So what do we do?

793
01:00:25,040 --> 01:00:26,540
