794
01:00:26,920 --> 01:00:30,980
Immediately apply voltage and create potential in the whole scheme.

795
01:00:31,160 --> 01:00:33,780
And current, meanwhile, hasn't come into it.

796
01:00:33,900 --> 01:00:36,780
It tries to pass into the circuit, but the iron doesn't let it.

797
01:00:37,220 --> 01:00:39,020
Delays its movement.

798
01:00:40,020 --> 01:00:48,580
At this moment we suddenly disconnect the circuit from the generator, from the source of dipolarity.

799
01:00:49,620 --> 01:00:57,540
Instead of it we place a semiconductor, a diode, so current passes only in this direction.

800
01:00:59,600 --> 01:01:02,420
Now our circuit with all its capacitance and potentials.

801
01:01:02,860 --> 01:01:06,160
We can run experiments to optimize it by connecting different devices.

802
01:01:09,180 --> 01:01:14,500
There's not that much energy in it — at least half of it will dissipate in the load.

803
01:01:14,620 --> 01:01:18,020
