808
01:01:37,800 --> 01:01:41,020
But the efficiency coefficient will automatically be more than one.

809
01:01:43,960 --> 01:01:49,240
You'll spend more energy powering the load than rotating the generator shaft.

810
01:01:50,500 --> 01:01:52,140
This is really feasible.

811
